	<div style="text-align:right;">
		TAMBOSI, Luciana Proceke<sup>1</sup>; ROSSI, Amelia do Carmo Sampaio<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
